&lt;&lt;You describe a wonderfully benevolent god that does no ill.&gt;&gt;<br>
<br>
I wanted to address this sentence because it is a typical non-believers response to an ignorant believer's statement <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Saying that God does no ill is a bit deceiving.  If you said God does no Evil, that is fairly clear-cut. But simply doing ill means doing harm.  And anyone who has briefly skimed the Old Testiment can attest to the fact that God has directly caused the harm of many people (ie Sodom and Gomorrah).  God is Good, but in the Old Testiment if you pissed him off he was as likely to toss down a bolt of lightning as call up a plague of locusts.  God is not your dotering grandfather who walks with a crutch and tends to forget where he's put his teeth!  <br>
<br>
I guess my point is this:  Christians should remember who it is they worship.  Non-believers should keep in mind that while we (christians) believe in a benevolent God, we also believe that God can and will punish us for our transgressions.  <br>
<br>
I expect a certain line of questions to result from this post... i'll try to answer them later.<br>
<br>
Stymp McStump <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=624.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=624.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=624.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=624.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=624.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=624.topic&start=121&stop=131>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=624.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=624.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=624.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=624.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.threadControl?topicID=624.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=624.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=624.topic>Unsubscribe</a>